      "updated": 1773666024710,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "|         | CommonJS | ES Modules (static) | ES Modules (dynamic) |\n| ------- | -------- | ------------------- | -------------------- |\n| Timing  | synchron | asynchron           | asynchron            |\n| Browser | ❌       | ✅                  | ✅                   |\n| Dynamic | dynamic  | static              | dynamic              |\n\n|                  | CommonJS | ES Modules (static) | ES Modules (dynamic) |\n| ---------------- | -------- | ------------------- | -------------------- |\n| Non-Blocking     | ❌       | ✅                  | ✅                   |\n| Optimized output | ❌       | ✅                  | ✅                   |\n| Tree-shakeable   | ❌       | ✅                  | ✅                   |\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "|         | CommonJS | ES Modules (static) | ES Modules (dynamic) |\n| ------- | -------- | ------------------- | -------------------- |\n| Timing  | synchron | asynchron           | asynchron            |\n| Browser | ❌       | ✅                  | ✅                   |\n| Dynamic | dynamic  | static              | dynamic              |\n\n|                  | CommonJS | ES Modules (static) | ES Modules (dynamic) |\n| ---------------- | -------- | ------------------- | -------------------- |\n| Non-Blocking     | ❌       | ✅                  | ✅                   |\n| Optimized output | ❌       | ✅                  | ✅                   |\n| Tree-shakeable   | ❌       | ✅                  | ✅                   |\n",
